# sovereign-mobility-systems
Industrial-grade autonomous mobility, energy-aware infrastructure, and sovereign transportation design. Simulation-first. Terrain-first. Infrastructure-aligned.
This repository focuses on:
- Terrain-first autonomy (not lane-following toys)
- Industrial, emergency, and sovereign use cases
- Energy-aware mobility systems
- Simulation-first development (no unsafe deployment claims)
https://github.com/
This is **not** a consumer vehicle project.
This is **infrastructure-scale mobility**.

---

## Scope

- Industrial autonomy (agriculture, mining, logistics)
- Emergency & priority transport (ambulance, fire, disaster response)
- Terrain-adaptive motion (uneven roads, drains, speed bumps)
- Energy-aware systems (waste heat, wireless transfer â€” where physically valid)
- Simulation-only research for non-deployable concepts

