## Development Philosophy

- Simulation before hardware
- Physics-respecting architecture
- Clear separation between deployable systems and research concepts
- No unsafe claims
- No consumer-market compromises

---

## Status

This repository is under active construction.
Files are added incrementally and may mutate as systems converge.

## Conceptual Context

This repository exists within a broader exploration of sovereign infrastructure,
industrial autonomy, and post-consumer mobility systems.

High-level philosophical and economic concepts are documented separately
and do not represent deployable claims within this repository.
